OL,3,CTemperatures set to plummet after
OL,4,Chottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FIt will still be cooler here on
OL,7,FThursday than it was on Wednesday, and
OL,8,Fless sunny too, but even so, highs of
OL,9,F20C or so are still likely.JHow cold
OL,10,Fcould it get?
OL,12,FTemperatures will fall away rapidly on
OL,13,FThursday night leading to the risk of
OL,14,Fa widespread frost.
OL,16,FBy Friday, daytime temperatures will
OL,17,Flikely only reach into the high single
OL,18,For low double figures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
