OL,3,CTemperatures set to plummet after
OL,4,Chottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FThere is also the chance of wintry
OL,7,Fshowers across the high ground of
OL,8,FScotland over the next few days.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FHow unusual is this temperature swing?
OL,17,FA high of 26.5C in early April is
OL,18,Fexceptional - but huge temperature
OL,19,Fswings in April are not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
