OL,3,CTemperatures set to plummet after
OL,4,Chottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FIn fact, perhaps more than any other,
OL,7,Fit's a month known for extremes with
OL,8,Fgreat leaps in temperature within just
OL,9,Fa few days and, interestingly, one of
OL,10,Fthe largest diurnal range's (the
OL,11,Fdifference between day and time time
OL,12,Ftemperatures) of the year.
OL,14,FWhen will it feel warm again?
OL,16,FAfter the last of the warm air has
OL,17,Fbeen pushed away from the southeast by
OL,18,Fthe end of Thursday, it's unlikely to
OL,19,Ffeel properly warm again until after
OL,20,Fthe weekend at least.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
