OL,3,CTemperatures set to plummet after
OL,4,Chottest day of the year so far
OL,6,FKeep watching the wind direction, when
OL,7,Fit backs south or southeasterly, it's
OL,8,Ftime to dig out the shorts and t-shirt
OL,9,Fagain.
